About Brick
Standard size of brick without morter = 242 mm x 114 mm x 70 mm
			= 9.5” X 4.5” X 2.75”
Standard size of brick with morter       = 254 mm x127 mm x76 mm							          = 10” x 5” x 3”		             
1cu.m brick = 410 Nos         [ cu.m = cubic meter ]			       	              1 cft brick	= 11.50 Nos 
3” wall per sft = 3 Nos
5” wall per sft = 5 Nos
10” wall per sft = 10 Nos
Ratio of 5” brick masonry   = 1:5
Ratio of 10” brick masonry = 1:6
B.F.S per sft   = 3 Nos        [ B.F.S = Brick Flat Soling ]
H.B.B per sft  = 5 Nos        [ H.B.B = Hearing Bone Bond ]
Amount of dry morter in brick masonry = Amount of brick masonry x .35
Volume of dry morter = Volume of wet morter x 1.50 or 1.54 

