Stair Formula
Formula : Rise 14 cm and Trade 30 cm. Then increase Rise@ 1 cm but decrease Trade @ 2 cm 
Formula : Trade + Rise       = 40 – 45 cm = 16” – 18”
Formula : Trade + 2 x Rise = 60 cm  =   24” 
Formula : Trade x Rise       = 400  – 450 cm2 
In Dormitory Building = 25 cm x 15 cm = 10” x 6”
In Public Building =  27 cm x 15 cm = 10.8” x 6’
In Hospital Building =  30 cm x 10 cm = 12” x 4”

